      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. can u get a bit more specific tho? like with hair and stuff. some of the execs have different hair textures or styles, so i wanna make sure i'm giving advice that actually helps them look the part. what kind of hair styles or grooming habits really convey that sense of 'control' you mentioned?",
